            <editorialDecl xml:lang="en">
                <p xml:lang="en">The original editorial practices followed by <ref target="http://shamela.ws/index.php/book/26523" xml:lang="en">
                  <foreign xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-ijmes">al-maktabat al-shāmila</foreign>
